---
title: AI Pipeline — Hold-to-Talk FSM & HTTP REST Flow
---
stateDiagram-v2

    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> Recording : button press (LOW edge)
    Recording --> Waiting : button release / 8s timeout
    Waiting --> Idle : button press (cancel)
    Waiting --> HTTPPhase : dataReady
    HTTPPhase --> Idle : finish / error
    HTTPPhase --> Waiting : cancel by button

    note left of Idle
        Poll button at 10ms
        No ISR, no explicit debounce
    end note
    note right of Recording
        JPEG captured on button press
        Mic INMP441: 16kHz, 16bit mono
        PSRAM buffer, max 8s
    end note
    note right of HTTPPhase
        Proactive WiFi starts during Recording
        Body: serializeJson(doc, client)
        SSE: char buffer per line
    end note
